[
  {
    "start": 0.24,
    "end": 1.44,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hello!"
  },
  {
    "start": 1.76,
    "end": 9.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** I'm sure that today in Washington DC, there are a lot of {great|素晴らしい/素晴らしい|/greɪt/|Great job today!} things to do."
  },
  {
    "start": 9.68,
    "end": 12.96,
    "text": "**Anna:** But I am not doing any of them."
  },
  {
    "start": 13.32,
    "end": 15.88,
    "text": "**Caty:** I'm sick."
  },
  {
    "start": 15.88,
    "end": 21.72,
    "text": "**Anna:** Right now, I'm going to {call|電話する/呼ぶ|/kɔːl/|Call me later.} my boss and tell her I cannot come into work."
  },
  {
    "start": 21.72,
    "end": 23.08,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hello."
  },
  {
    "start": 23.08,
    "end": 23.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** Ms."
  },
  {
    "start": 23.56,
    "end": 24.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** Weaver?"
  },
  {
    "start": 24.68,
    "end": 25.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hi."
  },
  {
    "start": 25.56,
    "end": 28.039,
    "text": "**Anna:** I can't come to work today."
  },
  {
    "start": 28.039,
    "end": 29.08,
    "text": "**Caty:** Why not?"
  },
  {
    "start": 29.08,
    "end": 30.68,
    "text": "**Caty:** What is wrong?"
  },
  {
    "start": 30.44,
    "end": 33.08,
    "text": "**Anna:** Well, yesterday I felt fine."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.08,
    "end": 36.36,
    "text": "**Anna:** In the morning, I {painted|絵を描いた/塗った|/ˈpeɪntɪd/|She painted the wall blue.} for hours."
  },
  {
    "start": 36.36,
    "end": 38.84,
    "text": "**Anna:** In the afternoon, I {cut|切った/刈った|/kʌt/|Cut the paper carefully.} wood."
  },
  {
    "start": 38.84,
    "end": 41.32,
    "text": "**Anna:** Then I built a {fire|火/燃料|/ˈfaɪər/|Build a fire for warmth.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 41.26,
    "end": 43.18,
    "text": "**Caty:** Anna, what do you mean?"
  },
  {
    "start": 43.18,
    "end": 45.66,
    "text": "**Caty:** Why can't you come to work today?"
  },
  {
    "start": 45.66,
    "end": 48.14,
    "text": "**Anna:** I do not feel well."
  },
  {
    "start": 48.14,
    "end": 48.78,
    "text": "**Anna:** I think"
  },
  {
    "start": 49.44,
    "end": 50.4,
    "text": "**Caty:** I'm sick."
  },
  {
    "start": 50.4,
    "end": 52.48,
    "text": "**Caty:** I'm sorry to hear that."
  },
  {
    "start": 52.48,
    "end": 55.04,
    "text": "**Caty:** I was sick last week too."
  },
  {
    "start": 55.04,
    "end": 56.88,
    "text": "**Caty:** I had the {flu|インフルエンザ|/fluː/|The flu is very contagious.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 58.44,
    "end": 60.2,
    "text": "**Anna:** What did you do?"
  },
  {
    "start": 60.2,
    "end": 64.92,
    "text": "**Anna:** I {slept|眠った|/slept/|I slept for eight hours.} a lot and I drank a lot of water."
  },
  {
    "start": 64.92,
    "end": 66.84,
    "text": "**Anna:** Do you have a doctor?"
  },
  {
    "start": 66.66,
    "end": 67.94,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yes, I do."
  },
  {
    "start": 67.94,
    "end": 69.94,
    "text": "**Caty:** You should {call|電話する/呼ぶ|/kɔːl/|Call the doctor now.} your doctor."
  },
  {
    "start": 69.94,
    "end": 71.94,
    "text": "**Caty:** And get lots of rest."
  },
  {
    "start": 71.94,
    "end": 72.66,
    "text": "**Anna:** Thanks, Ms."
  },
  {
    "start": 72.66,
    "end": 73.46,
    "text": "**Anna:** {Weaver|姓|/ˈwiːvər/|Ms. Weaver is a teacher}."
  },
  {
    "start": 73.46,
    "end": 74.979,
    "text": "**Anna:** I'll call right now."
  },
  {
    "start": 74.979,
    "end": 76.74,
    "text": "**Anna:** {Calling|電話をかける|/ˈkɔːlɪŋ/|I'm calling my friend.} my doctor."
  },
  {
    "start": 76.62,
    "end": 79.74,
    "text": "**Anna:** Now, where does this {thing|物/もの|/θɪŋ/|This thing is important.} go?"
  },
  {
    "start": 82.3,
    "end": 84.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hello, this is Dr."
  },
  {
    "start": 84.3,
    "end": 85.02,
    "text": "**Anna:** Bennett"
  },
  {
    "start": 84.9,
    "end": 86.34,
    "text": "**Anna:** How can I {help|助ける|/help/|Can I help you today?} you?"
  },
  {
    "start": 86.34,
    "end": 87.22,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hello, Dr."
  },
  {
    "start": 87.22,
    "end": 87.94,
    "text": "**Anna:** Bennett!"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.94,
    "end": 89.38,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is Anna!"
  },
  {
    "start": 89.38,
    "end": 91.14,
    "text": "**Anna:** Oh, hi Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 91.14,
    "end": 92.5,
    "text": "**Anna:** How can I help you?"
  },
  {
    "start": 92.5,
    "end": 94.74,
    "text": "**Anna:** I think I'm {sick|病気の|/sɪk/|I feel sick today}."
  },
  {
    "start": 94.2,
    "end": 96.84,
    "text": "**Anna:** Let me ask you a couple of {questions|質問|/ˈkwestʃənz/|I have some questions for you}."
  },
  {
    "start": 96.84,
    "end": 98.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** Do you have a {sore|痛い/腫れた|/sɔːr/|My throat is sore.} throat?"
  },
  {
    "start": 98.68,
    "end": 101.719,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yes, uh I have a sore throat."
  },
  {
    "start": 101.719,
    "end": 103.799,
    "text": "**Anna:** Do you have a {cough|咳|/kɒf/|He has a bad cough.}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 106.039,
    "end": 109.159,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yes, I have a cough."
  },
  {
    "start": 108.54,
    "end": 111.26,
    "text": "**Anna:** When did you start feeling sick?"
  },
  {
    "start": 111.26,
    "end": 112.62,
    "text": "**Anna:** This morning."
  },
  {
    "start": 112.62,
    "end": 115.58,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yesterday I felt great."
  },
  {
    "start": 115.58,
    "end": 118.7,
    "text": "**Anna:** In the morning I {painted|描いた|/ˈpeɪntɪd/|She painted a beautiful picture.} for hours."
  },
  {
    "start": 118.7,
    "end": 121.02,
    "text": "**Anna:** In the afternoon I {cut|切った|/kʌt/|I cut the paper.} wood."
  },
  {
    "start": 121.02,
    "end": 123.18,
    "text": "**Anna:** Uh {excuse|許してください|/ɪkˈskjuːz/|Excuse me, can I pass?} me, Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 123.06,
    "end": 125.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** But I don't need to know all that."
  },
  {
    "start": 125.3,
    "end": 126.98,
    "text": "**Anna:** Do you have a {fever|熱|/ˈfiːvər/|He has a high fever.}?"
  },
  {
    "start": 127.3,
    "end": 132.66,
    "text": "**Anna:** Oh, my {thermometer|体温計|/θərˈmɒmɪtər/|The thermometer shows my temperature.} says 125 degrees."
  },
  {
    "start": 132.66,
    "end": 133.3,
    "text": "**Caty:** What?"
  },
  {
    "start": 133.3,
    "end": 135.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yeah, that's not right."
  },
  {
    "start": 135.24,
    "end": 139.08,
    "text": "**Anna:** Oh wait, the {thermometer|体温計|/θərˈmɑːmɪtər/|Check your body temperature.} was in my {hot|熱い/高温の|/hɑːt/|The soup is very hot.} cup of coffee."
  },
  {
    "start": 139.08,
    "end": 141.8,
    "text": "**Anna:** Please take it again, Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 146.7,
    "end": 150.06,
    "text": "**Anna:** Okay, the thermometer says 100."
  },
  {
    "start": 150.06,
    "end": 151.26,
    "text": "**Anna:** 5 degrees."
  },
  {
    "start": 151.26,
    "end": 152.22,
    "text": "**Anna:** 100."
  },
  {
    "start": 152.22,
    "end": 154.94,
    "text": "**Anna:** 5 degrees is not too {high|高い/高熱}."
  },
  {
    "start": 154.74,
    "end": 157.14,
    "text": "**Anna:** I want you to drink lots of {water|水}."
  },
  {
    "start": 157.14,
    "end": 160.34,
    "text": "**Caty:** Rest in bed and get lots of {sleep|睡眠}."
  },
  {
    "start": 160.34,
    "end": 162.98,
    "text": "**Anna:** That is what my {boss|上司} said to do."
  },
  {
    "start": 162.76,
    "end": 166.44,
    "text": "**Anna:** Um doctor Bennett, when can I go to work?"
  },
  {
    "start": 166.44,
    "end": 168.92,
    "text": "**Anna:** Don't go to work for a couple of {days|日々}."
  },
  {
    "start": 168.92,
    "end": 169.72,
    "text": "**Anna:** Yes!"
  },
  {
    "start": 169.72,
    "end": 170.28,
    "text": "**Anna:** I mean"
  },
  {
    "start": 170.66,
    "end": 173.62,
    "text": "**Anna:** I don't want to make my {co-workers|同僚} sick."
  },
  {
    "start": 173.62,
    "end": 174.9,
    "text": "**Anna:** That's right."
  },
  {
    "start": 174.9,
    "end": 176.98,
    "text": "**Anna:** Call me back in a couple of days."
  },
  {
    "start": 176.98,
    "end": 177.7,
    "text": "**Anna:** I will, Dr."
  },
  {
    "start": 177.7,
    "end": 179.46,
    "text": "**Anna:** Bennett, and thanks."
  },
  {
    "start": 179.46,
    "end": 180.1,
    "text": "**Anna:** Well"
  },
  {
    "start": 180.46,
    "end": 184.3,
    "text": "**Anna:** You heard the doctor, no work for a couple of days."
  },
  {
    "start": 184.3,
    "end": 187.5,
    "text": "**Anna:** I need water, sleep, and um"
  },
  {
    "start": 188.24,
    "end": 190.08,
    "text": "**Caty:** Lots of movies!"
  },
  {
    "start": 190.96,
    "end": 197.44,
    "text": "**Anna:** Well the doctor didn't say anything about movies, but it can't {hurt|傷つける/害する}."
  },
  {
    "start": 197.44,
    "end": 198.8,
    "text": "**Anna:** Till next time"
  }
]
